{"title":"悼念许士杰","authors":["张报"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":9,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼念许士杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栋梁兰蕙一身兼①，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大平凡两德全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无畏无私公仆首②，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为时为事韵坛贤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方期华扁福音赐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不意瘟神噩耗传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"益友良师今痛失，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗笺再读倍凄然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"①领导干部兼诗人。②士杰同志曾被广州市民推举为“十大公仆”之首。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}